record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 992
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 992 -- (House of Representatives - May 01, 2008)

[Page: H2982]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to remove my name as a cosponsor of House Resolution 992.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentlewoman from Oklahoma?
